The 2.1.x-dev version of this module currently works on Drupal 10 and is being tested against Drupal 10 on a weekly basis. See https://www.drupal.org/pift-ci-job/2361649 for the most recent test results. The intention is to keep the development version of this module in sync with changes to core Drupal as Drupal 10 evolves.
